# ── Personal / sensitive ────────────────────────────────────
MEMORY.md
HARNESS_GUIDE.txt
THURSDAY_PROCEDURES.txt
WORKING_WITHOUT_CLAUDE.txt
*.pdf

# ── Personal knowledge domains ───────────────────────────────
knowledge/personal/
knowledge/career/
# Pattern: ignore all immediate children of knowledge/mtg/ (operational
# artifacts -- APL tuning, calibration logs, sim notes), then carve out
# strategy/ which contains general MTG theory blocks (Chapin principles,
# role theory, etc.) -- public/durable, not personal data.
# Git limitation: cannot re-include a child of a fully-ignored parent dir,
# so the parent rule must be `*`-glob not trailing-slash.
knowledge/mtg/*
!knowledge/mtg/strategy/

# ── Session state ────────────────────────────────────────────
state/
inbox/
logs/
dashboard.md

# ── Temp / cache ─────────────────────────────────────────────
agents/temp/
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo

# ── Auto-generated drift findings (daily; drift-detect -RouteFindings) ───────
# These pile up daily and are working artifacts, not curated knowledge. (One
# early file, drift-2026-04-28.md, was committed before this rule; leave it.)
knowledge/tech/drift-*.md

# ── Editor / OS ──────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
*.swp
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
